
## DateTimeBuddy Update \[2.0.6] - 2025-07-27

### Added

* `currentWeek()` — Returns start and end `DateTimeBuddy` instances for the current week (Mon–Sun).
* `nextWeek()` — Returns start and end of the next week.
* `previousWeek()` — Returns start and end of the previous week.
* `addWeeks(n: number)` — Adds `n` weeks to the instance.
* `subtractWeeks(n: number)` — Subtracts `n` weeks from the instance.
* Full test coverage for week navigation and boundary calculations.
* Console test output shows week logic with sample boundaries and shifted instances.

